name: Being Chased by The Procrastinator Demon
description:
Being chased and caught by a procrastinating demon was annoying. Whatever plan wanted to implement, suddenly, the enthusiasm disappeared. I have always thought that the demon might be driven by a shadow from wishful thinking and desire. Maybe this assumption was born because the time I spend daydreaming about what if is always longer than I spend working.

This is a token of appreciation for friends who still have and have not burned my work.
